# Platform AI (Hubdocs MCP)

- This repository builds the standalone `hubdocs` MCP; it is not a product
  docs/code hub.
- Do not keep `platform-repos.json` or cross-repository topology here.
- Package-owned source, tools, installers, harness, tests, and release docs are
  the scope; see `/platform-ai`.
- Product maps live in destination hubs. Hubdocs may merge only its owned skill
  IDs during destination `init`.
- Never depend on sibling checkout layout or copy another MCP's harness.
